{"thag2.35:0.1":"Theragatha 2.35 ","thag2.35:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.35:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag2.35:0.4":"Sambulakaccanattheragatha ","thag2.35:1.1":"“Devo ca vassati, devo ca galagalayati, ","thag2.35:1.2":"Ekako caham bherave bile viharami; ","thag2.35:1.3":"Tassa mayham ekakassa bherave bile viharato, ","thag2.35:1.4":"Natthi bhayam va chambhitattam va lomahamso va. ","thag2.35:2.1":"Dhammata mamesa yassa me, ","thag2.35:2.2":"Ekakassa bherave bile; ","thag2.35:2.3":"Viharato natthi bhayam va, ","thag2.35:2.4":"Chambhitattam va lomahamso va”ti. ","thag2.35:2.5":"… Sambulakaccano thero …. "}